                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-45-victim504 t18210606-45-viclabel257"></join>; the prisoner had been discharged from a regiment of Veterans a few days before. I was billetted at the <placeName id="t18210606-45-crimeloc258">King's Arms, Westminster</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18210606-45-crimeloc258" type="placeName" value="King's Arms, Westminster"></interp>
