                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18210606-45-off255 t18210606-45-crimeloc258"></join>. On the 21st of April, he slept in the same room with me. I went out about ten o'clock to parade, and when I returned I missed my shirts - I had seen them an hour before. I found him in ten minutes, with both my shirts on his back, over his own.</p>
